Description: Handle of Knidian pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp; trident symbol.
Type series: KT720 (in Grace's unpublished Knidian Type series)
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.175, 12. Name, Theudamos.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0318)
